title: I Raced Across The Ocean
author: JackManifoldTV
description:
Me & Nihachu raced Tubbo & Wilbur Soot across the ocean! This was CRAZY!!

The rules are simple: we race in teams of two across the channel and to the Isle of Wight (France). Whoever loses has to throw something they care about into the ocean and lose it FOREVER!!

Come watch Jack Manifold on the big screen (aka Twitch) - https://www.twitch.tv/JackManifoldTV 

Edited by: @Wheatskins   

@Tubbo @Niki Nihachu @Wilbur Soot 

Follow my Twitter - @JackManifoldTV 
Follow my Instagram - @JackManifoldTV

ルールは簡単で、2人1組で海峡を渡り、ワイト島（フランス）までレースをする。負けた人は、自分の大切なものを海に捨てて、永遠に失ってしまうのです。

ジャック・マニフォールドを大画面（通称Twitch）で見よう！ - https://www.twitch.tv/JackManifoldTV

我和Nihachu与Tubbo和Wilbur Soot在大洋彼岸比赛! 这真是太疯狂了！!

规则很简单：我们两个人一组，横跨海峡，到怀特岛（法国）比赛。谁输了，就得把他们关心的东西扔进海里，永远失去它！！。
